                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Lists preliminary results (those received before the paper's publication)
                    from the congressional and presidential elections, including the vote totals
                    received by each candidate from each township in Franklin County. The editor
                    says that, although not all the votes for the president's race are in, it looks
                    as if Lincoln has won. The results in both races are: ANTRIM--Coffroth (423),
                    Koontz (431), McClellan (0), Lincoln (24); CHAMBERSBURG, NORTH WARD--Coffroth
                    (140), Koontz (251), McClellan (0), Lincoln (135); CHAMBERSBURG, SOUTH
